WEBVTT

00:02.669 --> 00:04.035
Ohh, yeah!

00:04.037 --> 00:06.705
♪ Powerpuff Girls
fighting crime ♪

00:06.707 --> 00:09.341
♪ To save the world
before bedtime ♪

00:09.343 --> 00:11.777
♪ Here's the time to shine
when you're fighting crime ♪

00:11.779 --> 00:13.545
♪ Power it up ♪
♪ Who's got the power? ♪

00:13.547 --> 00:15.013
♪ We got the power ♪

00:15.015 --> 00:17.215
♪ Breaking through the wall,
gonna do it all ♪

00:17.217 --> 00:19.418
♪ We don't quit ♪
♪ Who's got the power? ♪

00:19.420 --> 00:21.052
♪ We got the power ♪

00:21.054 --> 00:23.455
Oh! Yeah!

00:23.476 --> 00:26.544
♪♪

00:32.346 --> 00:34.880
Castle Fluffernoodle
is officially open.

00:34.882 --> 00:37.315
Good location,
nice neighborhood,

00:37.317 --> 00:38.516
low property taxes.

00:38.518 --> 00:39.784
This will sell easy.

00:41.021 --> 00:43.255
Oh, no! My castle!

00:43.257 --> 00:44.589
Buttercup!

00:44.591 --> 00:45.724
Hold on!

00:45.726 --> 00:49.361
My heavy metal detector
says I'm getting close.

00:49.363 --> 00:50.762
[ Guitar riff plays ]

00:50.764 --> 00:52.430
Jackpot!

00:52.833 --> 00:54.666
[ Chuckles ] Huh?

00:54.668 --> 00:57.102
Aw, butt cheeks! A can!

00:57.104 --> 00:59.104
Don't you people recycle?

00:59.539 --> 01:01.406
Ohh!
Huh?

01:01.408 --> 01:03.675
Buttercup,
you're not the only one

01:03.677 --> 01:05.110
on the beach, you know.

01:05.112 --> 01:06.945
Unfortunately,
I do know that.

01:06.947 --> 01:09.748
And hopefully,
one of these losers had this.

01:09.750 --> 01:12.884
A 1974 Duke-a-Cola
bottle cap.

01:12.886 --> 01:14.786
Giddy-up and go!

01:14.788 --> 01:17.022
And this cap
is the last one left

01:17.024 --> 01:18.390
to complete my collection.

01:18.392 --> 01:20.792
This bottle cap
is supes rare.

01:20.794 --> 01:22.394
Supes, bloss!

01:22.396 --> 01:24.396
[ Groans ]
Come on, Bubbles.

01:24.398 --> 01:26.064
Let's go for a dip.

01:26.066 --> 01:27.799
♪♪

01:27.801 --> 01:29.801
Cannonball!

01:29.803 --> 01:31.369
Belly flap!

01:31.371 --> 01:32.570
Belly flap?

01:32.572 --> 01:34.239
[ Whistle! ]
Aah!

01:34.241 --> 01:36.541
Ouch!

01:36.543 --> 01:39.411
[ Both giggle ]

01:39.413 --> 01:41.046
Huh?
Huh?

01:41.048 --> 01:42.414
[ All gasp ]

01:42.416 --> 01:45.617
Jeremy?
I'm cool.

01:46.620 --> 01:51.890
Girls, someone has stolen
all the water in Townsville!

01:51.892 --> 01:52.857
[ Sloop! ]

01:54.494 --> 01:57.662
Uh, don't worry, mayor.
We're on it.

02:00.100 --> 02:01.599
Hmm.

02:01.601 --> 02:03.969
Looks like all the water
was sucked up through this pipe.

02:03.971 --> 02:05.904
But what sort of
criminal mastermind

02:05.906 --> 02:07.572
could have done
such a thing?

02:07.574 --> 02:11.276
Who? Who?!<i> Who?!</i>

02:11.278 --> 02:12.477
[ Sighs ]

02:12.479 --> 02:14.946
I'm afraid
this case is un-solvable.

02:14.948 --> 02:17.415
Bubbles,
it's written right here.

02:17.417 --> 02:19.084
Man Boy.

02:19.086 --> 02:20.585
Uh, Man Boy?

02:20.587 --> 02:24.122
Was he that guy that opened up
that dog gymnasium?

02:24.124 --> 02:25.290
No! Man Boy!

02:25.292 --> 02:27.959
Powers of a man,
body of a boy.

02:27.961 --> 02:29.461
He's a super villain.

02:29.463 --> 02:31.830
Oh, yeah!

02:31.832 --> 02:34.099
We need to get
Townsville's water back.

02:34.101 --> 02:36.868
Follow these pipes,
and we find Man Boy.

02:36.870 --> 02:38.837
Isn't that right,
Buttercup?

02:38.839 --> 02:40.705
[ Laughs ]

02:40.707 --> 02:43.508
You are mine, Duke-a-Col--
Huh?

02:43.510 --> 02:46.144
A gold medal? Junk!

02:46.146 --> 02:47.979
Buttercup!

02:47.981 --> 02:49.481
Coming!

02:49.483 --> 02:52.751
♪♪

02:56.823 --> 03:00.325
[ Laughs evilly ]

03:00.327 --> 03:02.694
Those prissy-pants
Powerpuff Girls

03:02.696 --> 03:04.929
think they can take
<i> my</i> water?!

03:07.034 --> 03:10.502
I harvested that water
fair and square

03:10.504 --> 03:12.303
with my own bare hands

03:12.305 --> 03:14.239
for one manly purpose --

03:14.241 --> 03:18.510
my lawn!

03:18.512 --> 03:20.178
[ Grunts ]

03:20.180 --> 03:22.881
Drink, my mighty lawn!

03:22.883 --> 03:24.315
Drink!

03:24.317 --> 03:27.852
Let's see if those puny girls
think they're tough enough

03:27.854 --> 03:31.322
to take the water
from my kung-fu grip.

03:31.324 --> 03:32.424
[ Whip! ]

03:32.426 --> 03:34.559
Behold my manly army!

03:34.561 --> 03:37.028
[ Engine starts ]

03:37.030 --> 03:39.497
Hogs on Hogs...

03:39.499 --> 03:40.698
Man: [ Grunts ]

03:40.700 --> 03:42.734
...Logger jacks...

03:42.736 --> 03:44.736
I say,
care for a spot of tea?

03:44.738 --> 03:46.704
Thank you, Mr. Thomas.

03:46.706 --> 03:49.407
...And some British Guys!

03:49.409 --> 03:51.543
Uh, why did I hire them?

03:51.545 --> 03:54.446
We are an economic power.

03:54.448 --> 03:56.414
Oh, yeah. Ugh.

03:56.416 --> 03:57.949
So, my army,

03:57.951 --> 04:03.054
go crush
those namby-pamby girls!

04:03.056 --> 04:05.223
Fly, my ripped creatures!

04:05.225 --> 04:09.294
Fly! Fly-y-y-y!

04:09.296 --> 04:11.896
[ All shouting indistinctly ]

04:11.898 --> 04:13.364
[ Indistinct conversation ]

04:13.366 --> 04:14.866
[ Bicycle bell rings ]

04:16.436 --> 04:18.803
Okay, we've been
through Crater Canyon,

04:18.805 --> 04:21.639
Grandma's Gulch,
and Petey's Pituitary Perch.

04:21.641 --> 04:23.575
Man Boy's lair
should be up ahead.

04:23.577 --> 04:24.709
Let me see!

04:24.711 --> 04:27.212
Hmm.
Look what I can do.

04:27.214 --> 04:30.215
♪♪

04:30.217 --> 04:35.753
Call me Cap'n Bubbles,
Scourge of the Seven Seas.

04:35.755 --> 04:37.589
All right, let's move on.

04:37.591 --> 04:39.491
Yay!
Buttercup!

04:39.493 --> 04:40.725
Coming.

04:40.727 --> 04:43.995
Arr, this be the way,
matey.

04:45.132 --> 04:48.766
Hmm. Seems quiet.

04:48.768 --> 04:51.102
A little<i> too</i> quiet.

04:51.104 --> 04:54.606
I know. I can sing
an ol' sea shanty.

04:54.608 --> 04:55.940
Sea shanty?

04:55.942 --> 04:58.443
Bubbles, we're in
the middle of a desert.

04:58.445 --> 05:00.778
Desert be a kind of sea.

05:00.780 --> 05:02.680
Hmm. Where's Buttercup?

05:02.682 --> 05:03.882
[ Ray gun zaps ]

05:06.153 --> 05:07.852
[ Indistinct shouting ]

05:07.854 --> 05:11.422
Looks like we be
walkin' the plank, matey.

05:11.424 --> 05:14.692
[ Metal detector whirring ]

05:18.698 --> 05:20.932
[ Metal detector buzzes ]

05:21.334 --> 05:22.467
[ Up-tempo heavy metal plays ]

05:22.469 --> 05:25.136
♪ Aw, yeah ♪

05:25.138 --> 05:26.437
[ Gasps ]

05:26.439 --> 05:30.208
Aw, my heavy metal detector's
at full face melt.

05:30.210 --> 05:31.910
This could be it!

05:33.813 --> 05:36.314
Ha! I found it!

05:36.316 --> 05:37.615
Finally!

05:37.617 --> 05:41.186
A 1974 Duke-a-Cola
bottle cap!

05:41.188 --> 05:43.488
Howdy, partner!

05:43.490 --> 05:45.723
Ohh.

05:45.725 --> 05:46.858
He, he, he, he!

05:46.860 --> 05:49.561
Ha! Check it out, guys!

05:50.030 --> 05:51.062
Guys?

05:52.465 --> 05:54.866
Blossom? Bubbles?

05:56.136 --> 05:57.635
Where are you?

06:02.375 --> 06:03.575
A bow?

06:03.577 --> 06:05.043
Blossom.

06:05.045 --> 06:07.512
And a perfect
three-pointed pirate hat?

06:07.514 --> 06:09.314
Bubbles.

06:09.316 --> 06:11.149
[ Wind howls ]

06:11.151 --> 06:14.085
Aw, Duke,
Man Boy took my sisters.

06:14.087 --> 06:17.388
I should have been here.
Yeah, you shoulda.

06:17.390 --> 06:19.023
I know. I screwed up.

06:19.025 --> 06:21.759
Well, it's no time
for a pity party.

06:21.761 --> 06:25.563
It's time to put on your focus
and go get your sisters.

06:25.565 --> 06:28.866
You're right.
Now, giddy-up and go!

06:28.868 --> 06:32.670
Yeah.
Giddy-up and go!

06:36.743 --> 06:39.277
These are great carvings.

06:39.679 --> 06:41.779
I think the bear traps
are kind of overkill.

06:41.781 --> 06:43.681
[ Engine revs in distance ]

06:48.555 --> 06:50.288
[ Both screaming ]

06:51.091 --> 06:54.259
[ Laughs evilly ]

06:54.261 --> 06:58.696
Not so tough,
are you, Powerpuff Girls?

06:59.366 --> 07:02.233
Give back the water
you stole from Townsville!

07:02.235 --> 07:04.302
A man doesn't give.

07:04.304 --> 07:05.570
He takes.

07:05.572 --> 07:07.138
With muscle!

07:07.140 --> 07:08.873
And brawn!

07:11.244 --> 07:14.212
[ Both coughing ]

07:14.214 --> 07:15.647
♪ Man boy ♪

07:15.649 --> 07:16.914
Pretty cool, huh?

07:16.916 --> 07:18.950
[ Scoffs ] Not really.

07:18.952 --> 07:21.486
Are you<i> kidding</i> me?!

07:21.488 --> 07:23.154
That was amazing!

07:23.156 --> 07:26.124
Bubbles, stop supporting
the bad guys!

07:26.126 --> 07:29.927
We prefer to be called
the<i> Man</i> Guys!

07:29.929 --> 07:32.630
[ Groans ]
So, what is this all about?

07:32.632 --> 07:35.333
You just wanted
to show us your new toy?

07:35.335 --> 07:36.501
This isn't a toy!

07:36.503 --> 07:38.436
[ Tires squeal ]

07:38.438 --> 07:39.671
Ha!

07:39.673 --> 07:42.340
This is how
I take care of my lawn!

07:45.445 --> 07:47.345
[ Grunts ]

07:47.347 --> 07:49.247
[ Grunting ]

07:52.452 --> 07:53.618
[ Boing! ] [ Cuckoo! ]

07:53.620 --> 07:56.421
[ Grunting ]

07:58.825 --> 08:00.124
[ Squealing ]

08:00.126 --> 08:02.327
[ Engine revs ]
[ Trumpets blare ]

08:02.329 --> 08:03.695
Hoo-ah!

08:03.697 --> 08:06.130
[ Laughs evilly ]

08:06.132 --> 08:09.934
And it's how
I'll take care of you!

08:10.370 --> 08:12.837
[ Tires screech ]

08:12.839 --> 08:14.939
I hope Buttercup
shows up soon.

08:14.941 --> 08:17.375
Yeah, she'd love this!

08:20.146 --> 08:23.114
Huh?
Someone's on my lawn.

08:23.116 --> 08:24.849
Yeah. Me.

08:24.851 --> 08:27.385
Also, there's a pile
of dog doo over there.

08:27.387 --> 08:28.419
What?

08:29.155 --> 08:31.823
You're going down,
Man Boy!

08:31.825 --> 08:34.892
[ Laughs evilly ]

08:34.894 --> 08:36.761
Get her, boys!

08:40.333 --> 08:41.799
[ Pig squeals ]

08:41.801 --> 08:43.735
[ All shouting ]

08:45.472 --> 08:46.671
Take that.
Take that.

08:46.673 --> 08:48.172
And that's for you.
Take that.

08:48.174 --> 08:50.708
Sorry. Sorry.
That.

08:50.710 --> 08:52.844
Aah!

08:52.846 --> 08:55.079
[ All screaming ]

08:58.385 --> 09:02.286
That is a really nice lawnmower.
Bubbles!

09:04.858 --> 09:07.392
Time for the main course,
huh?!

09:08.695 --> 09:10.828
Things are about to get --

09:10.830 --> 09:11.829
Hairy?

09:11.831 --> 09:14.065
Quit taking my lines!

09:18.405 --> 09:19.404
Huh?

09:19.406 --> 09:21.439
Ohh!
Time for a shave.

09:23.176 --> 09:24.842
[ Gasps ]

09:24.844 --> 09:26.944
Hmm. That's better.

09:30.383 --> 09:32.250
Ha! Missed!

09:32.252 --> 09:34.318
Aah! Mist!

09:41.561 --> 09:42.794
[ Both screaming ]

09:42.796 --> 09:44.562
[ Laughs evilly ]

09:44.564 --> 09:47.565
Looks like
this rodeo's over, partner.

09:47.567 --> 09:49.133
Not yet it's not.

09:49.702 --> 09:53.337
♪♪

09:54.574 --> 09:55.873
[ Laughs evilly ]

09:55.875 --> 09:58.576
Goodbye, prissy-pants!
[ Tires squeal ]

09:58.578 --> 10:00.745
[ Both screaming ]

10:00.747 --> 10:02.580
You're never
gonna make it!

10:02.582 --> 10:04.382
I'm not, but you are!

10:04.384 --> 10:04.982
Wait, what?

10:04.984 --> 10:07.385
Giddy-up and go!

10:07.387 --> 10:09.053
Waaaah!

10:12.592 --> 10:14.425
[ Engine sputters ]

10:14.427 --> 10:15.460
Huh?

10:16.329 --> 10:17.462
My lawn!

10:17.464 --> 10:21.999
My precious,
precious la-a-a-awn!

10:24.671 --> 10:26.971
Look who finally showed up.

10:26.973 --> 10:30.608
Sorry,
I-I was being selfish.

10:30.610 --> 10:34.011
Well, you gave up your
bottle cap to save us.

10:34.013 --> 10:35.980
Yeah,
'cause I finally decided

10:35.982 --> 10:37.949
to focus on
the right things.

10:37.951 --> 10:39.784
Leather jackets?

10:39.786 --> 10:42.553
Why do I bare my soul to you,
Bubbles?

10:45.992 --> 10:46.824
Mr. Mayor!

10:46.826 --> 10:48.292
Ooh, girls!

10:48.294 --> 10:51.295
While you were gone,
the lake came back on!

10:51.297 --> 10:53.197
Uh...

10:53.199 --> 10:55.132
No problem, Mr. Mayor.

10:55.134 --> 10:57.435
You can finish
your bath now.

10:57.437 --> 10:59.103
Bath? What bath?

10:59.105 --> 11:01.272
Uh... Hey. Ohh.

11:03.042 --> 11:04.709
♪ Powerpuff girls
fighting crime ♪

11:04.711 --> 11:07.311
♪ Saving the world
before bedtime ♪

11:07.313 --> 11:10.147
♪ Battling evil toe-to-toe ♪

11:10.149 --> 11:14.252
♪ Saving the day,
a Powerpuff goal ♪
